ph\" },\n 94 |       { from: \"graph\", to: \"repo\" },\n 95 |       { from: \"repo\", to: \"triage\" }\n 96 |     ],\n 97 |     logs: [\n 98 |       { time: \"11:20:01\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Connecting to EHR secure registry...\" },\n 99 |       { time: \"11:20:03\", type: \"event\", msg: \"Query ingested: Trial eligibility for patient #PX-8821\" },\n100 |       { time: \"11:20:04\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Extraction Agent] Aggregating biomarkers and lab histories...\" },\n101 |       { time: \"11:20:06\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Semantic Graph] Traversing clinical knowledge graph (420K nodes)...\" },\n102 |       { time: \"11:20:10\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Privacy Guard] Enforcing data consent boundary checks...\" },\n103 |       { time: \"11:20:11\", type: \"success\", msg: \"Inquiry resolved. Synthesis delivered with provenance links.\" }\n104 |     ]\n105 |   },\n106 |   {\n107 |     id: \"manufacturing\",\n108 |     name: \"Manufacturing AI Factory\",\n109 |     category: \"IoT Telemetry & Industrial Automation\",\n110 |     description: \"Modernizing manufacturing assembly pipelines and global logistics networks by deploying agent networks directly onto shop-floor edge computing servers and machine telemetry gateways.\",\n111 |     outcomeThemes: {\n112 |       fasterDecisionMaking: \"Processes live edge telemetry in milliseconds to execute safety shutoffs and routing changes instantly.\",\n113 |       reducedManualEffort: \"Automates parts reservation lists, repair ticket drafts, and warehouse stock requisitions.\",\n114 |       betterKnowledgeAccess: \"Centralizes machine logs, enabling technical staff to search machine historical anomalies in normal language.\",\n115 |       improvedComplianceWorkflows: \"Ensures continuous safety monitoring against strict environmental and operational guidelines.\",\n116 |       improvedEmployeeExperience: \"Maintenance technicians receive automated troubleshooting briefs, sparing them from sorting through PDFs.\"\n117 |     },\n118 |     nodes: [\n119 |       { id: \"edge\", label: \"Industrial IoT Gateway\", desc: \"Streams live high-frequency telemetry from sensors.\", x: 15, y: 50 },\n120 |       { id: \"diag\", label: \"Predictive Diagnosis Agent\", desc: \"Identifies anomalies and computes wear indicators.\", x: 40, y: 50 },\n121 |       { id: \"stock\", label: \"Logistics Coordinator\", desc: \"Coordinates parts inventory across regional nodes.\", x: 65, y: 50 },\n122 |       { id: \"maint\", label: \"ERP Maintenance Bridge\", desc: \"Generates automated work orders and dispatches.\", x: 90, y: 50 }\n123 |     ],\n124 |     connections: [\n125 |       { from: \"edge\", to: \"diag\" },\n126 |       { from: \"diag\", to: \"stock\" },\n127 |       { from: \"stock\", to: \"maint\" }\n128 |     ],\n129 |     logs: [\n130 |       { time: \"14:15:30\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Connected to Factory Assembly Line 4 Edge Gateway...\" },\n131 |       { time: \"14:15:32\", type: \"event\", msg: \"Telemetry alert: Turbine vibration spike registered (490Hz)\" },\n132 |       { time: \"14:15:33\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Diagnostics] Analyzing vibration curves against machine logs...\" },\n133 |       { time: \"14:15:36\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Logistics] Interrogating local warehouse replacement registries...\" },\n134 |       { time: \"14:15:39\", type: \"system\", msg: \"OSHA safety verified. Dispatched preventive work order.\" },\n135 |       { time: \"14:15:40\", type: \"success\", msg: \"Work order confirmed. Parts reserved in Row 4. Zero downtime.\" }\n136 |     ]\n137 |   },\n138 |   {\n139 |     id: \"retail\",\n140 |     name: \"Retail Agent Operations\",\n141 |     category: \"Omnichannel Logic & Forecasting\",\n142 |     description: \"Aligning digital shopper behavior tracking, inventory redistribution pipelines, and automated multi-channel localized promotions into a cohesive retail demand fulfillment system.\",\n143 |     outcomeThemes: {\n144 |       fasterDecisionMaking: \"Reroutes supply-chain shipments dynamically based on localized retail demand fluctuations.\",\n145 |       reducedManualEffort: \"Replaces traditional manual inventory reports with autonomous re-routing distribution lists.\",\n146 |       betterKnowledgeAccess: \"Bridges logistics databases, historical promotions, and online search metrics into one engine.\",\n147 |       improvedComplianceWorkflows: \"Ensures automated compliance audits on localized promotional pricing rules dynamically.\",\n148 |       improvedEmployeeExperience: \"Fulfillment planners manage inventory via natural language inquiries rather than dense sheets.\"\n149 |     },\n150 |     nodes: [\n151 |       { id: \"omni\", label: \"Omnichannel Ingestion\", desc: \"Integrates point-of-sale data and online cart feeds.\", x: 15, y: 50 },\n152 |       { id: \"demand\", label: \"Demand Forecaster Agent\", desc: \"Predicts local depletion risk and behavior trends.\", x: 40, y: 50 },\n153 |       { id: \"logis\", label: \"Fulfillment Logic Core\", desc: \"Optimizes warehouse inventory reallocations.\", x: 65, y: 50 },\n154 |       { id: \"promo\", label: \"Sovereign Campaign Optimizer\", desc: \"Triggers and optimizes local marketing messages.\", x: 90, y: 50 }\n155 |     ],\n156 |     connections: [\n157 |       { from: \"omni\", to: \"demand\" },\n158 |       { from: \"demand\", to: \"logis\" },\n159 |       { from: \"logis\", to: \"promo\" }\n160 |     ],\n161 |     logs: [\n162 |       { time: \"16:40:45\", type: \"system\", msg: \"Syncing regional omnichannel demand registers...\" },\n163 |       { time: \"16:40:46\", type: \"event\", msg: \"Sales spike detected: winter outerwear range (Northeast Hub)\" },\n164 |       { time: \"16:40:48\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Forecaster] Stock depletion risk forecasted within 72 hours.\" },\n165 |       { time: \"16:40:49\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Logistics] Re-routing 1,400 surplus units from East Hub.\" },\n166 |       { time: \"16:40:53\", type: \"agent\", msg: \"[Promo] Deploying local targeted consumer campaigns.\" },\n167 |       { time: \"16:40:55\", type: \"success\", msg: \"Logistics update confirmed. Target campaign activated.\" }\n168 |     ]\n169 |   }\n170 | ];\n171 | \n172 | export default function ClientSuccessSection() {\n173 |   const [activePatternId, setActivePatternId] = useState<string>(\"banking\");\n174 |   const [activeTab, setActiveTab] = useState<\"architecture\" | \"video\">(\"architecture\");\n175 |   const [hoveredNode, setHoveredNode] = useState<ArchitectureNode | null>(null);\n176 |   \n177 |   const [streamedLogs, setStreamedLogs] = useState<ConsoleLog[]>([]);\n178 |   const [isPlaying, setIsPlaying] = useState<boolean>(true);\n179 |   const [playSpeed, setPlaySpeed] = useState<number>(1000);\n180 |   const logIndexRef = useRef<number>(0);\n181 |   const timerIdRef = useRef<NodeJS.Timeout | null>(null);\n182 | \n183 |   const activePattern = REPRESENTATIVE_PATTERNS.find(p => p.id === activePatternId) || REPRESENTATIVE_PATTERNS[0];\n184 | \n185 |   useEffect(() => {\n186 |     setHoveredNode(null);\n187 |   }, [activePatternId]);\n188 | \n189 |   const startLogStream = useCallback(() => {\n190 |     if (timerIdRef.current) clearInterval(timerIdRef.current);\n191 | \n192 |     timerIdRef.current = setInterval(() => {\n193 |       const logs = activePattern.logs;\n194 |       const index = logIndexRef.current;\n195 | \n196 |       if (index < logs.length) {\n197 |         setStreamedLogs(prev => [...prev, logs[index]]);\n198 |         logIndexRef.current = index + 1;\n199 |       } else {\n200 |         setStreamedLogs([logs[0]]);\n201 |         logIndexRef.current = 1;\n202 |       }\n203 |     }, playSpeed);\n204 |   }, [activePattern.logs, playSpeed]);\n205 | \n206 |   useEffect(() => {\n207 |     setStreamedLogs([activePattern.logs[0]]);\n208 |     logIndexRef.current = 1;\n209 |     \n210 |     if (timerIdRef.current) {\n211 |       clearInterval(timerIdRef.current);\n212 |     }\n213 | \n214 |     if (isPlaying) {\n215 |       startLogStream();\n216 |     }\n217 | \n218 |     return () => {\n219 |       if (timerIdRef.current) clearInterval(timerIdRef.current);\n220 |     };\n221 |   }, [activePattern.logs, isPlaying, startLogStream]);\n222 | \n223 |   const handleTogglePlay = () => {\n224 |     if (isPlaying) {\n225 |       if (timerIdRef.current) clearInterval(timerIdRef.current);\n226 |       setIsPlaying(false);\n227 |     } else {\n228 |       setIsPlaying(true);\n229 |     }\n230 |   };\n231 | \n232 |   const handleResetStream = () => {\n233 |     setStreamedLogs([activePattern.logs[0]]);\n234 |     logIndexRef.current = 1;\n235 |     if (isPlaying) {\n236 |       startLogStream();\n237 |     }\n238 |   };\n239 | \n240 |   return (\n241 |     <motion.section \n242 |       initial={{ opacity: 0 }}\n243 |       whileInView={{ opacity: 1 }}\n244 |       viewport={{ once: true }}\n245 |       transition={{ duration: 1 }}\n246 |       className=\"w-full bg-[#020202] px-6 lg:px-16 lg:py-32 py-20 relative overflow-hidden\"\n247 |     >\n248 |       <div className=\"absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none\" style={{ backgroundImage: \"radial-gradient(circle at 100% 50%, #E9882805 0%, transparent 40%)\" }} />\n249 |       \n250 |       <div className=\"max-w-[1795px] mx-auto relative z-10\">\n251 |         \n252 |         {/* Section Heading */}\n253 |         <div className=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end justify-between gap-6 mb-16\">\n254 |           <SectionHeading\n255 |             title={\n256 |               <h2 className=\"text-[32px] sm:text-[44px] leading-none font-bold text-left uppercase text-white tracking-widest\">\n257 |                 CLIENT <span className=\"text-[#E98828]\">SUCCESS</span>\n258 |               </h2>\n259 |             }\n260 |             titleClassName=\"text-left\"\n261 |             dividerWidthClassName=\"w-[300px]\"\n262 |           />\n263 |           <div className=\"max-w-xl\">\n264 |             <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[#E98828] border border-[#E98828]/20 px-2 py-0.5 rounded bg-[#E98828]/5 mb-3 inline-block\">\n265 |               REPRESENTATIVE BLUEPRINTS\n266 |             </span>\n267 |             <p className=\"text-[#A0A0A0] text-[14px] font-light leading-relaxed\">\n268 |               To safeguard client confidentiality, we publish exclusively anonymized representative architecture blueprints actively deployed in sovereign enterprise operations. No fictional client entities, no inflated marketing stats.\n269 |             </p>\n270 |           </div>\n271 |         </div>\n272 | \n273 |         {/* Categories Tab Selector */}\n274 |         <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 mb-12 overflow-x-auto scrollbar-none flex gap-2 md:gap-4 pb-2\">\n275 |           {REPRESENTATIVE_PATTERNS.map((pattern) => {\n276 |             const isActive = pattern.id === activePatternId;\n277 |             return (\n278 |               <button\n279 |                 key={pattern.id}\n280 |                 onClick={() => setActivePatternId(pattern.id)}\n281 |                 className={`flex items-center gap-3 px-5 py-3.5 rounded-t-xl border-t border-x transition-all shrink-0 cursor-pointer text-left ${\n282 |                   isActive \n283 |                     ? \"bg-[#0A0A0A] border-white/10 text-[#E98828] shadow-lg\" \n284 |                     : \"bg-transparent border-transparent text-[#707070] hover:text-[#A0A0A0]\"\n285 |                 }`}\n286 |               >\n287 |                 <div className=\"text-sm\">\n288 |                   <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono tracking-widest uppercase block text-[#707070]\">\n289 |                     {pattern.category}\n290 |                   </span>\n291 |                   <span className=\"text-[14px] font-bold tracking-tight\">\n292 |                     {pattern.name}\n293 |                   </span>\n294 |                 </div>\n295 |                 {isActive && (\n296 |                   <span className=\"relative flex h-2 w-2 ml-2\">\n297 |                     <span className=\"animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-[#E98828] opacity-75\"></span>\n298 |                     <span className=\"relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-[#E98828]\"></span>\n299 |                   </span>\n300 |                 )}\n301 |               </button>\n302 |             );\n303 |           })}\n304 |         </div>\n305 | \n306 |         {/* Main Grid Workspace */}\n307 |         <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-8 items-stretch\">\n308 |           \n309 |           {/* Left panel: Narrative Case Study Details and Outcomes Matrix */}\n310 |           <div className=\"lg:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-between space-y-8\">\n311 |             \n312 |             {/* Case Study Details */}\n313 |             <div className=\"bg-[#060606] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8\">\n314 |               <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#E98828] tracking-widest uppercase block mb-1\">\n315 |                 REPRESENTATIVE CASE STUDY\n316 |               </span>\n317 |               <h3 className=\"text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white mb-4\">\n318 |                 {activePattern.name}\n319 |               </h3>\n320 |               <p className=\"text-[#A0A0A0] text-[15px] font-light leading-relaxed\">\n321 |                 {activePattern.description}\n322 |               </p>\n323 |             </div>\n324 | \n325 |             {/* Outcome Matrix Block */}\n326 |             <div className=\"bg-[#060606] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8\">\n327 |               <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between border-b border-white/5 pb-4 mb-6\">\n328 |                 <h4 className=\"text-xs font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-[#707070]\">\n329 |                   BUSINESS OUTCOME THEMES\n330 |                 </h4>\n331 |                 <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#707070]\">\n332 |                   VERIFIED DEPLOYED SYSTEM CAPABILITIES\n333 |                 </span>\n334 |               </div>\n335 |               \n336 |               <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-5\">\n337 |                 {Object.entries(activePattern.outcomeThemes).map(([key, outcome]) => {\n338 |                   let title = \"\";\n339 |                   switch (key) {\n340 |                     case \"fasterDecisionMaking\":\n341 |                       title = \"Faster Decision Making\";\n342 |                       break;\n343 |                     case \"reducedManualEffort\":\n344 |                       title = \"Reduced Manual Effort\";\n345 |                       break;\n346 |                     case \"betterKnowledgeAccess\":\n347 |                       title = \"Better Knowledge Access\";\n348 |                       break;\n349 |                     case \"improvedComplianceWorkflows\":\n350 |                       title = \"Improved Compliance Workflows\";\n351 |                       break;\n352 |                     case \"improvedEmployeeExperience\":\n353 |                       title = \"Improved Employee Experience\";\n354 |                       break;\n355 |                   }\n356 | \n357 |                   return (\n358 |                     <div key={key} className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-[#0A0A0A] hover:border-white/10 hover:bg-[#0E0E0E] transition-all group\">\n359 |                       <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2 mb-2\">\n360 |                         <span className=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#E98828]\" />\n361 |                         <h5 className=\"text-[13px] font-bold tracking-tight text-white group-hover:text-[#E98828] transition-colors\">\n362 |                           {title}\n363 |                         </h5>\n364 |                       </div>\n365 |                       <p className=\"text-[12px] text-[#808080] font-light leading-relaxed\">\n366 |                         {outcome}\n367 |                       </p>\n368 |                     </div>\n369 |                   );\n370 |                 })}\n371 | \n372 |                 {/* Directory Link Card */}\n373 |                 <div className=\"p-4 rounded-xl border border-[#E98828]/10 bg-gradient-to-br from-[#E98828]/5 to-transparent flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[110px] group\">\n374 |                   <div>\n375 |                     <h5 className=\"text-[13px] font-bold text-white tracking-tight uppercase\">\n376 |                       Architecture Library\n377 |                     </h5>\n378 |                     <p className=\"text-[11px] text-[#A0A0A0] font-light mt-1\">\n379 |                       Explore detailed blueprints and agent profiles across the full library.\n380 |                     </p>\n381 |                   </div>\n382 |                   <Link \n383 |                     href=\"/resources/case-studies\"\n384 |                     className=\"text-[11px] font-mono text-[#E98828] group-hover:text-white transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 mt-3\"\n385 |                   >\n386 |                     Browse Case Studies Directory <span>→</span>\n387 |                   </Link>\n388 |                 </div>\n389 | \n390 |               </div>\n391 |             </div>\n392 | \n393 |           </div>\n394 | \n395 |           {/* Right panel: Active Preview Workspace (Architecture SVG or Live Simulation Video) */}\n396 |           <div className=\"lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col bg-[#060606] border border-white/5 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden min-h-[480px]\">\n397 |             {/* Header */}\n398 |             <div className=\"border-b border-white/5 px-4 py-3 bg-[#0A0A0A] flex items-center justify-between shrink-0\">\n399 |               <div className=\"flex items-center gap-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono text-[#707070] tracking-widest uppercase\">\n400 |                 <span className=\"w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/50 animate-pulse\" />\n401 |                 DEPLOYMENT WORKSPACE\n402 |               </div>\n403 |               <div className=\"flex bg-[#020202] rounded-lg p-0.5 border border-white/5 font-mono text-[9px]\">\n404 |                 <button onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"architecture\")} className=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded cursor-pointer text-white\">BLUEPRINT</button>\n405 |                 <button onClick={() => setActiveTab(\"video\")} className=\"px-2.5 py-1 rounded cursor-pointer text-white\">SIMULATOR</button>\n406 |               </div>\n407 |             </div>\n408 | \n409 |             {/* Content: Architecture */}\n410 |             {activeTab === \"architecture\" ? (\n411 |               <div className=\"p-6 flex flex-col justify-between flex-grow\">\n412 |                 <div>\n413 |                   <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#707070] tracking-widest uppercase block mb-1\">SYSTEM TOPOLOGY</span>\n414 |                   <p className=\"text-[12px] text-[#808080] font-light leading-relaxed mb-4\">Hover nodes to inspect runtime boundaries.</p>\n415 |                   <div className=\"bg-[#020202] rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-4 flex items-center justify-center min-h-[160px]\">\n416 |                     <svg width=\"100%\" height=\"100\" viewBox=\"0 0 100 100\" className=\"w-full h-auto overflow-visible select-none\">\n417 |                       <marker id=\"arrow\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"6\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"6\" markerHeight=\"6\" orient=\"auto-start-reverse\"><path d=\"M 0 2 L 8 5 L 0 8 z\" fill=\"#303030\" /></marker>\n418 |                       {activePattern.connections.map((conn, idx) => {\n419 |                         const fromNode = activePattern.nodes.find(n => n.id === conn.from);\n420 |                         const toNode = activePattern.nodes.find(n => n.id === conn.to);\n421 |                         if (!fromNode || !toNode) return null;\n422 |                         return (\n423 |                           <g key={idx}>\n424 |                             <line x1={`${fromNode.x}%`} y1={`${fromNode.y}%`} x2={`${toNode.x}%`} y2={`${toNode.y}%`} stroke=\"#1A1A1A\" strokeWidth=\"2\" markerEnd=\"url(#arrow)\" />\n425 |                             <line x1={`${fromNode.x}%`} y1={`${fromNode.y}%`} x2={`${toNode.x}%`} y2={`${toNode.y}%`} stroke=\"#E98828\" strokeWidth=\"1.5\" strokeDasharray=\"4 12\" className=\"animate-[dash_4s_linear_infinite]\" />\n426 |                           </g>\n427 |                         );\n428 |                       })}\n429 |                       {activePattern.nodes.map((node) => {\n430 |                         const isHovered = hoveredNode?.id === node.id;\n431 |                         return (\n432 |                           <g key={node.id} className=\"cursor-help\" onMouseEnter={() => setHoveredNode(node)} onMouseLeave={() => setHoveredNode(null)}>\n433 |                             <circle cx={`${node.x}%`} cy={`${node.y}%`} r={isHovered ? \"7%\" : \"4.5%\"} fill={isHovered ? \"rgba(233, 136, 40, 0.15)\" : \"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02)\"} stroke={isHovered ? \"#E98828\" : \"#303030\"} strokeWidth=\"1\" className=\"transition-all duration-300\" />\n434 |                             <circle cx={`${node.x}%`} cy={`${node.y}%`} r=\"1.5%\" fill={isHovered ? \"#E98828\" : \"#A0A0A0\"} />\n435 |                             <text x={`${node.x}%`} y={`${node.y - 7}%`} textAnchor=\"middle\" fill={isHovered ? \"#E98828\" : \"#606060\"} className=\"text-[3.5px] font-mono uppercase font-bold\">{node.label.split(\" \")[0]}</text>\n436 |                           </g>\n437 |                         );\n438 |                       })}\n439 |                     </svg>\n440 |                   </div>\n441 |                 </div>\n442 |                 <div className=\"bg-[#020202] border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-4 min-h-[120px] flex flex-col justify-center mt-4\">\n443 |                   <AnimatePresence mode=\"wait\">\n444 |                     {hoveredNode ? (\n445 |                       <motion.div key={hoveredNode.id} initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 5 }} animate={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }} exit={{ opacity: 0, y: -5 }} transition={{ duration: 0.15 }}>\n446 |                         <h4 className=\"text-[12px] font-mono uppercase text-[#E98828] font-bold mb-1\">{hoveredNode.label}</h4>\n447 |                         <p className=\"text-[11px] text-[#A0A0A0] leading-relaxed\">{hoveredNode.desc}</p>\n448 |                       </motion.div>\n449 |                     ) : (\n450 |                       <div className=\"text-center py-2\">\n451 |                         <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#505050] uppercase tracking-wider block\">HOVER BLUEPRINT NODES TO INSPECT LOGIC</span>\n452 |                       </div>\n453 |                     )}\n454 |                   </AnimatePresence>\n455 |                 </div>\n456 |               </div>\n457 |             ) : (\n458 |               /* Content: Video simulator console */\n459 |               <div className=\"p-6 flex flex-col justify-between flex-grow\">\n460 |                 <div>\n461 |                   <div className=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-2\">\n462 |                     <span className=\"text-[10px] font-mono text-[#707070] tracking-widest uppercase\">AGENT EXECUTION STREAM</span>\n463 |                     <span className=\"text-[9px] font-mono text-[#E98828] animate-pulse\">● LIVE OPERATIONAL</span>\n464 |                   </div>\n465 |                   <p className=\"text-[12px] text-[#808080] font-light leading-relaxed mb-4\">Simulated agent runtime execution demonstrating continuous multi-agent system handoffs.</p>\n466 |                   <div className=\"bg-[#020202] rounded-xl border border-white/5 p-4 min-h-[190px] max-h-[190px] overflow-y-auto font-mono text-[10px] leading-relaxed flex flex-col justify-end\">\n467 |              